reviews.review_text:
flat tire don't usually write negativities,  but the wheel is flat,  or  got  stuck with a sharp tack,  between  the  overblown  effects  and lousy levels  and totally out of  tune,  i had to stop listening and say,  you'll definitely want to skip the wheel

the other jerry tunes  are tolerable or  sometime decent, but not  enough  inspiration to match all the perspiration here,  don't smell  too good if you're sniffing
